item.title: Help please wont take long! its about when u die u spawn at wild53 lava. help!
item.dc:creator: @Telenim Telenim
item.description:
@Telenim wrote:

Turn caps lock off before you do anything.

Search for the coordinates in client.java at the exact location of where you go when you die (Mage Arena apparently) and change them to Edgeville bank coordinates or whatever you want.

Don’t mess with the client too much if you don’t know what you’re doing. Java is also required to run your client, so make sure he has Java, and if he has a different Java version tell him to change the paths in the Run.bat or whatever it uses to run. If that isn’t the error, ask him if anything in the black box happens, like gives him an error and post it here.

Read full topic
